&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Heat blowing varken(party)&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Hunt for the Chief of Varken&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;You might have already seen him several times, didn't you? I am talking about the Varken which is blowing such an amazing heat off. I'd say, this is probably the chief of the Lava Varken of that area. The heat blown off by it is so hot, we can't even approach him. Can you hunt him down for us please? This is not a usual monster. I promise you a great reward. 

 Ahh, as I told you, it is very difficult to hunt it down. It will probably be better for you to do it with a party of people you know. Go ahead.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Why are you hesitating? However I have nobody else to rely on. No one other than you. I am very sorry.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;I asked for a lot of requests. But this is the most amazing case. Here is your well deserved reward.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
