&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;The Cause of the Disease&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Ca&amp;#xE7;ar Lure Stone Treant&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;N&amp;#xF3;s terminamos de analisar o Lure Stone Treant Spore. Como eu esperava, o Spore &amp;#xE9; carregado pelo ar e entra no corpo da pessoa, e ent&amp;#xE3;o ela come&amp;#xE7;a a endurecer como uma pedra. Felizmente foi prescrito um rem&amp;#xE9;dio aos moradores, ent&amp;#xE3;o agora eles est&amp;#xE3;o se recuperando. Mas o Spore continua no ar. Precisamos prevenir isto eliminando o Lure Stone Treant em Droes Dungeon agora mesmo.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Tenha cuidado para n&amp;#xE3;o inalar o Spore que est&amp;#xE1; flutuando no ar.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Se reduzirmos o n&amp;#xFA;mero delas, ser&amp;#xE1; dif&amp;#xED;cil para sa&amp;#xED;rem de Droes Dungeon. Mesmo que saiam, n&amp;#xE3;o &amp;#xE9; necess&amp;#xE1;rio se preocupar pois ser&amp;#xE1; um n&amp;#xFA;mero baixo.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</newversion></questtextxml></ec1ym701a></diff><new><scrxmas01> scrxmas01</scrxmas01><scrxmas02> scrxmas02</scrxmas02><scrxmas03> scrxmas03</scrxmas03><scrxmas04> scrxmas04</scrxmas04><scrxmas05> scrxmas05</scrxmas05><scrxmas06> scrxmas06</scrxmas06><scrxmas07> scrxmas07</scrxmas07><scrxmas08> scrxmas08</scrxmas08></new><settings><searchkey> questlistid</searchkey><ignore> id</ignore><columnnametable> </columnnametable><parsexml> </parsexml></settings></server_questtext_PT></number68><number69><server_questtext_TR><diff><bc2gt005a><questtextxml><oldversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;How to overcome heat&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Pepper ile sohbet&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Lava Plateau'nun &amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131; inan&amp;#x131;lmazd&amp;#x131;r. Canavar avlarken normalden daha fazla yoruldum. 

 Benim ad&amp;#x131;ma Miss Pepper'a bu &amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131;yla nas&amp;#x131;l ba&amp;#x15F;a &amp;#xE7;&amp;#x131;kabilece&amp;#x11F;imi sorar m&amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131;n? Di&amp;#x11F;er insanlarla birlikte gidip canavar avlamal&amp;#x131;y&amp;#x131;m. Yine &amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131; y&amp;#xFC;z&amp;#xFC;nden ac&amp;#x131; &amp;#xE7;ekece&amp;#x11F;iz belli ki. Yolu &amp;#xE7;abuk &amp;#x15F;ekilde g&amp;#xFC;venlik alt&amp;#x131;na almal&amp;#x131;y&amp;#x131;z. Umar&amp;#x131;m benim ad&amp;#x131;ma &amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131;yla nas&amp;#x131;l ba&amp;#x15F;a &amp;#xE7;&amp;#x131;k&amp;#x131;labilece&amp;#x11F;ini &amp;#xF6;&amp;#x11F;renirsin.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Bir yolu varsa &amp;#xE7;ok iyi. E&amp;#x11F;er hi&amp;#xE7;bir yolu yoksa yapabilece&amp;#x11F;imiz bir &amp;#x15F;ey yok.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Uzun zamand&amp;#x131;r g&amp;#xF6;r&amp;#xFC;nm&amp;#xFC;yorsun. Bug&amp;#xFC;n ne var ne yok?&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
