&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;How to overcome heat&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Pepper ile sohbe&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Lava Plateau'nun &amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131; inan&amp;#x131;lmazd&amp;#x131;r. Canavar avlarken normalden daha fazla yoruldum. 

 Benim ad&amp;#x131;ma Miss Pepper'a bu &amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131;yla nas&amp;#x131;l ba&amp;#x15F;a &amp;#xE7;&amp;#x131;kabilece&amp;#x11F;imi sorar m&amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131;n? Di&amp;#x11F;er insanlarla birlikte gidip canavar avlamal&amp;#x131;y&amp;#x131;m. Yine &amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131; y&amp;#xFC;z&amp;#xFC;nden ac&amp;#x131; &amp;#xE7;ekece&amp;#x11F;iz belli ki. Yolu &amp;#xE7;abuk &amp;#x15F;ekilde g&amp;#xFC;venlik alt&amp;#x131;na almal&amp;#x131;y&amp;#x131;z. Umar&amp;#x131;m benim ad&amp;#x131;ma &amp;#x131;s&amp;#x131;yla nas&amp;#x131;l ba&amp;#x15F;a &amp;#xE7;&amp;#x131;k&amp;#x131;labilece&amp;#x11F;ini &amp;#xF6;&amp;#x11F;renirsin.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Bir yolu varsa &amp;#xE7;ok iyi. E&amp;#x11F;er hi&amp;#xE7;bir yolu yoksa yapabilece&amp;#x11F;imiz bir &amp;#x15F;ey yok.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Uzun zamand&amp;#x131;r g&amp;#xF6;r&amp;#xFC;nm&amp;#xFC;yorsun. Bug&amp;#xFC;n ne var ne yok?&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</newversion></questtextxml></bc2gt005a><bc2gt005d><questtextxml><oldversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;found preparation(2)&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;&amp;#xD6;zel yap&amp;#x131;m ilac&amp;#x131; Kent'e verme&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Groop Amca bekledi&amp;#x11F;im kadar iyi &amp;#xE7;&amp;#x131;kt&amp;#x131;. San&amp;#x131;r&amp;#x131;m Groop Amca Lava Plateau ve Shifty'yi biliyordu de&amp;#x11F;il mi? Her neyse, bug&amp;#xFC;n &amp;#xF6;nemli bir &amp;#x15F;ey &amp;#xF6;&amp;#x11F;renmi&amp;#x15F; oldun. 

 &amp;#x130;&amp;#x15F;te sana Pepper'dan &amp;#xF6;zel yap&amp;#x131;m ila&amp;#xE7;.  L&amp;#xFC;tfen bunu B&amp;#xFC;y&amp;#xFC;k birader Kent'e g&amp;#xF6;t&amp;#xFC;r.  E&amp;#x11F;er ileride ihtiyac&amp;#x131;n olursa l&amp;#xFC;tfen beni ziyaret et. Sana daha ucuza satar&amp;#x131;m.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;B&amp;#xFC;y&amp;#xFC;k birader Kent seni bekliyor.  Git ve hemen ona ver.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Bu Lava varken'in derisi mi? Bunu Miss. Pepper'a verece&amp;#x11F;im. Kesinlikle &amp;#xE7;ok iyi bir i&amp;#x15F; &amp;#xE7;&amp;#x131;kard&amp;#x131;n.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</oldversion><newversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
