&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Elimination of an anxiety Element&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Retis Avla&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Hey, duydu&amp;#x11F;uma g&amp;#xF6;re Droes'de bir fare s&amp;#xFC;r&amp;#xFC;s&amp;#xFC; varm&amp;#x131;&amp;#x15F;. Buralarda g&amp;#xF6;r&amp;#xFC;nm&amp;#xFC;yorlar m&amp;#x131;? Hum, ama nedense rahats&amp;#x131;z oluyorum. Fare s&amp;#xFC;r&amp;#xFC;s&amp;#xFC;n&amp;#xFC; yok edebilir misin? Buraya gelmiyolar ama ya say&amp;#x131;lar&amp;#x131; artarsa? Ya de&amp;#x11F;erli gemimin etraf&amp;#x131;n&amp;#x131; sararlarsa, hay&amp;#x131;r!&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Haha. Gemimin etraf&amp;#x131;na gelirler diye endi&amp;#x15F;e etmiyorum.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Geri mi d&amp;#xF6;nd&amp;#xFC;n? &amp;#x130;&amp;#x15F;te &amp;#xF6;d&amp;#xFC;l&amp;#xFC;n. L&amp;#xFC;tfen onlar&amp;#x131; yok et ki say&amp;#x131;lar&amp;#x131; artmas&amp;#x131;n.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
