</oldversion><newversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Scattered Report(2)&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Frogy Raporunu Teslim Et&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Asl&amp;#x131;na bakarsan bu raporu ba&amp;#x15F;kan Briant'tan &amp;#xF6;d&amp;#xFC;n&amp;#xE7; ald&amp;#x131;k. Bu, ba&amp;#x15F;kan&amp;#x131;n yazd&amp;#x131;&amp;#x11F;&amp;#x131; Cherrytown ortak raporu. Bir kopyas&amp;#x131; yok, bu y&amp;#xFC;zden kaybedersek mahvoluruz.  E&amp;#x11F;er raporu ve daha fazla bilgi getirdiysen ba&amp;#x15F;kan &amp;#xE7;ok sinirlenmez. Ama onunla kar&amp;#x15F;&amp;#x131;lacak y&amp;#xFC;z&amp;#xFC;m yok, bu y&amp;#xFC;zden l&amp;#xFC;tfen bunlar&amp;#x131; ba&amp;#x15F;kana benim yerime sen g&amp;#xF6;t&amp;#xFC;r.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Yabanc&amp;#x131;lar&amp;#x131; i&amp;#x15F;e al&amp;#x131;rken l&amp;#xFC;tfen daha dikkatli olal&amp;#x131;m. Nerde senin gibi bir yetenek&amp;#x2026;.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Ms. Coco hile yap&amp;#x131;yor. Ver bana. Coco'ya s&amp;#xF6;yle k&amp;#x131;zg&amp;#x131;n de&amp;#x11F;ilim, endi&amp;#x15F;elenmesine gerek yok. Hahaha.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</newversion></questtextxml></ef1yh006b><ef1yh007a><questtextxml><oldversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
