&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;The Cause of the Disease&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Otuz Lure Stone Treant Avla&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Lure Stone Treant Spore'u ara&amp;#x15F;t&amp;#x131;rma i&amp;#x15F;ini bitirdik. Tahmin etti&amp;#x11F;im gibi bu Spore havada dolan&amp;#x131;yor ve v&amp;#xFC;cudun i&amp;#xE7;ine i&amp;#x15F;liyor, sonra da v&amp;#xFC;cut bir ta&amp;#x15F; gibi sertle&amp;#x15F;iyor. Baz&amp;#x131; ila&amp;#xE7;lar sayesinde hastalar iyile&amp;#x15F;iyor, tedavileri yap&amp;#x131;l&amp;#x131;rsa tamamen iyile&amp;#x15F;ecekler. Fakat Spore'lar er ya da ge&amp;#xE7; havada yay&amp;#x131;lacak. Yay&amp;#x131;lmalar&amp;#x131;n&amp;#x131; &amp;#xF6;nlememiz gerek. Droes Dungeon'a git ve Lure Stone Treant'i &amp;#x15F;imdi yok et.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Havadaki Spore'u i&amp;#xE7;ine &amp;#xE7;ekmemeye dikkat et.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;E&amp;#x11F;er say&amp;#x131;lar&amp;#x131;n&amp;#x131; biraz azaltabilirsek Droes Dungeon'dan &amp;#xE7;&amp;#x131;kmalar&amp;#x131; zorla&amp;#x15F;acak. &amp;#xC7;&amp;#x131;ksalar bile endi&amp;#x15F;elenmen gerekmez &amp;#xE7;&amp;#xFC;nk&amp;#xFC; say&amp;#x131;lar&amp;#x131;n&amp;#x131;n azalmas&amp;#x131; iyi bir &amp;#x15F;ey.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</newversion></questtextxml></ec1ym701a></diff><new><scrxmas01> scrxmas01</scrxmas01><scrxmas02> scrxmas02</scrxmas02><scrxmas03> scrxmas03</scrxmas03><scrxmas04> scrxmas04</scrxmas04><scrxmas05> scrxmas05</scrxmas05><scrxmas06> scrxmas06</scrxmas06><scrxmas07> scrxmas07</scrxmas07><scrxmas08> scrxmas08</scrxmas08></new><settings><searchkey> questlistid</searchkey><ignore> id</ignore><columnnametable> </columnnametable><parsexml> </parsexml></settings></server_questtext_TR></number69><number70><server_questtext_TW><diff><bc2gt005a><questtextxml><oldversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
