&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;The damage of earthquake occurrence(2)&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Depremin verdi&amp;#x11F;i zararla ilgili raporu Matthew'a teslim et&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Hi&amp;#xE7;bir fikrin yok ama belki de &amp;#xE7;ok tehlikeli &amp;#x15F;eyler olacak. Bu bir 'ihtimal' ama yine de olabilir. Bu kopyay&amp;#x131; &amp;#xF6;nceden Matthew'a yolla.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;&amp;#xD6;nsezilerim pek kuvvetli de&amp;#x11F;il.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Seni buraya hangi r&amp;#xFC;zgar att&amp;#x131;?&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
