&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Request of a Shy Girl&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Amalrie ile konu&amp;#x15F;&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Vaktin var m&amp;#x131;? Bana &amp;#xF6;yle bakma, seni o kadar &amp;#xE7;ok &amp;#xE7;al&amp;#x131;&amp;#x15F;t&amp;#x131;rmaya niyetim yok. Amalrie'yi tan&amp;#x131;yormusun? Burada bartender olarak &amp;#xE7;al&amp;#x131;&amp;#x15F;&amp;#x131;yor. Yard&amp;#x131;ma ihtiyac&amp;#x131; var. E&amp;#x11F;er bo&amp;#x15F; vaktin varsa, git onu g&amp;#xF6;r!&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Biraz bekle &amp;#x15F;imdi. Bundan sonra seni bir at gibi &amp;#xE7;al&amp;#x131;&amp;#x15F;t&amp;#x131;raca&amp;#x11F;&amp;#x131;m.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Ah, buraya m&amp;#x131; geldin&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
</newversion></questtextxml></ef1yh004a><ef1yh004b><questtextxml><oldversion> &lt;?xml version="1.0"?&gt;
