&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Amalrie's Tea for Fatigue Recovery&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Jewel-Leaf Topla&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Um&amp;#x2026; &amp;#xC7;ok yorgun g&amp;#xF6;r&amp;#xFC;n&amp;#xFC;yorsun. Bu y&amp;#xFC;zden sana bir iyilik yapmay&amp;#x131; d&amp;#xFC;&amp;#x15F;&amp;#xFC;n&amp;#xFC;yorum. Jewel otun var m&amp;#x131;? Duydu&amp;#x11F;uma g&amp;#xF6;re Jewel-Leef ile kaynat&amp;#x131;lan &amp;#xE7;ay yorgunlu&amp;#x11F;a iyi gelirmi&amp;#x15F;. Bana onu getirirsen senin i&amp;#xE7;in kaynat&amp;#x131;r&amp;#x131;m. Ve e&amp;#x11F;er istersen, bunu Cell Craft'dan toplaya bilirsin.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Art&amp;#x131;k endi&amp;#x15F;elenme. Test sona erdi.&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;Oh. &amp;#xC7;ok fazla getimi&amp;#x15F;sin. Kendini yorgun hissetti&amp;#x11F;inde bana u&amp;#x11F;ra.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
