&lt;Questtext&gt;&lt;Title&gt;Report Improvement&lt;/Title&gt;&lt;Mission1&gt;Auder Second Generation Report Topla&lt;/Mission1&gt;&lt;Mission2&gt;&lt;/Mission2&gt;&lt;Mission3&gt;&lt;/Mission3&gt;&lt;desc&gt;Magistri'den &amp;#xE7;ok gizli resmi bir belge geldi.  Auder Second Gerneration i&amp;#xE7;in haz&amp;#x131;rlanan bir bilgi bu. Kahretsin, ihmal ettim, eskiden yoktu. Auder Second Gerneration'&amp;#x131; nereden biliyorlard&amp;#x131; ki?  Her neyse, ben ara&amp;#x15F;t&amp;#x131;raca&amp;#x11F;&amp;#x131;m, o halde yapal&amp;#x131;m m&amp;#x131; ne dersin? Git ve Auder Second Gerneration bilgilerini ara. &amp;#xD6;d&amp;#xFC;l yeterli gelecektir.&lt;/desc&gt;&lt;preDlg&gt;&lt;/preDlg&gt;&lt;startDlg&gt;&lt;/startDlg&gt;&lt;runDlg&gt;Her &amp;#x15F;eyi ayn&amp;#x131; anda m&amp;#x131; vermem gerek?&lt;/runDlg&gt;&lt;finishDlg&gt;&amp;#xD6;nemli de&amp;#x11F;il. Bana yine yard&amp;#x131;m et.&lt;/finishDlg&gt;&lt;/Questtext&gt;
